  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version: `1.6.6` (version mist autoupdates)\r\nOS & Version: Windows 10 64bit\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\nGeth should not interfere with mouse. \r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\nMouse cursor disapears, jumps to lower right corner of screen, clicks register but cursor not visible and mouse pos does not change.\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\n- Mouse: Zelotes 5500 \r\n\r\n#### Additional Info\r\n--nousb \"fixes\" the problem, but since i bought a ledger nano i can't use it with geth.\r\nI'm happy to test tweaked versions of geth\r\nAlso i have the problem on two different win10 computers. but with the same mouse models.",
